# Task Completion Notification

When you have finished a multi-step task, finished applying code changes, or completed a long-running process, run this command to notify the user:

```
osascript -e 'display notification "I have finished the task! ✅" with title "Cursor Agent" sound name "Glass"'
```

Always run this command after completing such tasks.
